Cyberpunk style: A massive hexagonal server tower rises through layers of neon-lit fog in a dark industrial cityscape. The tower is constructed from stacked, glowing container modules in electric blue and deep purple, each module connected by pulsing data cables that snake between them like luminous veins. At the tower's core, a bright orange debugging beam cuts vertically through all layers, illuminating the internal circuitry visible through translucent panels. Holographic diagnostic displays float around the structure, showing cascading code patterns and connection nodes. The scene is viewed from a low angle, emphasizing the towering stack of interconnected modules against a rain-streaked sky filled with distant server farms and communication spires. Steam rises from ventilation ports, catching the neon glow. The mood is technical yet atmospheric, suggesting deep system inspection within a complex layered architecture.
